      <title>加拿大的盟军黄金在纽约证券交易所上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/canada-s-allied-gold-seeks-listing-on-new-york-stock-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大的盟军黄金公司已开始申请纽约证券交易所上市的过程，并加入了全球最高厅的整个行业迁移。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/canada-s-allied-gold-seeks-listing-on-new-york-stock-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 16:14:54 GMT</pubDate>
